# status — human-facing rollup

Posted by the orchestrator at the close of every wave: one line per task
(done / blocked / gate-not-met) plus anything currently open. This is the
"are we on track at a glance" summary layer — the five per-agent
build.logs (plus orchestrator.log) remain the detailed record for when
you want to go deeper on any one line here. Newest entries at the bottom.
Do not delete or rewrite prior entries.

