is live at https://rythdg.github.io/LitList/ (GitHub Pages, deployed
via the now-real CI/CD workflows). GitHub Pages deploy is green. The
human still needs to (1) confirm all Render env vars are filled in
(TURSO_*, ZOTERO_*, SESSION_COOKIE_SECRET, TOKEN_ENCRYPTION_KEY,
FRONTEND_ORIGINS — see logs/creds.log and render.yaml), (2) update the
